#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.greater_equal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.greater\\_equal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:1 of
msgid "Return the truth value of (x1 >= x2) element-wise."
msgstr "返回 (x1 >= x2) 的逐元素布尔值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:7 of
msgid ""
"Input tensors.  If ``x1.shape != x2.shape``, they must be broadcastable "
"to a common shape (which may be the shape of one or the other)."
msgstr ""
"输入张量。如果 ``x1.shape != x2.shape``，它们必须可以广播到一个共同形状（"
"可能是其中一个的形状）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，它的形状必须与输入广播后的形状一致"
"。如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数"
"）的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Array of bools, or a single bool if `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr "**out** -- 布尔数组，如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 是标量，则返回单个布尔值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.greater_equal.greater_equal:24 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`greater`, :py:obj:`less`, :py:obj:`less_equal`, :py:obj:`equal`,"
" :py:obj:`not_equal`"
msgstr ""

